						<h4>Jess deCourcy Hinds</h4>
												<p>Jess deCourcy Hinds is a writer and librarian in NYC. Her work has been featured in numerous outlets, from NPR to the New York Times' Modern Love column to literary journals such as Quarterly West. She works as a youth librarian at two Title 1 schools, and teaches graduate-level courses on children's literature. Photo credit: Doug Weiner.</p>
